                  </hi>. I am the wife of the last witness—I saw the prisoner there on the Saturday morning and went to the till and found a bad florin—there was no other florin there—next evening the prisoner Came again and had some spirits—he was charged with passing a bad florin the day before, and I said "You are the man;" he said I was never here before."</p>
